node.text:
Had the most hectic but fruitful April of my life ! 
No kidding! #WFH is like sprinting in a marathon ... non stop.. #stayhomeForWork ..
Was missing chilling out n tea/coffee ... Then my son @reallobang had them delivered to me.#feelingloved.xoxo  My fuel of happiness n energy for May 2020 ! I Am Ready ! Thank you @enchantedcafe its so yumzzzx no bluff u k ! 
#circuitbreakersg
#littleactsoflove
